{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":860,"text":"As a kid I always loved information"},{"time":3739,"text":"that I could get from data"},{"time":5587,"text":"and the stories that could be told with numbers."},{"time":8629,"text":"I remember, growing up, I'd be frustrated at"},{"time":10913,"text":"how my own parents would lie to me using numbers."},{"time":16459,"text":"\"Talithia, if I've told you once \nI've told you a thousand times.\""},{"time":21443,"text":"No dad, you've only told me 17 times"},{"time":25335,"text":"and twice it wasn't my fault. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28497,"text":"I think that is one of the reasons I got a Ph.D. in statistics."},{"time":31661,"text":"I always wanted to know,"},{"time":32569,"text":"what are people trying to hide with numbers?"},{"time":35755,"text":"As a statistician,"},{"time":36938,"text":"I want people to show me the data"},{"time":40791,"text":"so I can decide for myself."},{"time":43126,"text":"Donald and I were pregnant with our third child"},{"time":46175,"text":"and we were at about 41 and a half weeks,"},{"time":48909,"text":"what some of you may refer to as being overdue."},{"time":52286,"text":"Statisticians, we call that"},{"time":54121,"text":"being within the 95 percent confidence interval."},{"time":56807,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":58673,"text":"And at this point in the process"},{"time":60951,"text":"we had to come in every couple of days"},{"time":63144,"text":"to do a stress test on the baby,"},{"time":64952,"text":"and this is just routine,"},{"time":66134,"text":"it tests whether or not the baby \nis feeling any type of undue stress."},{"time":70720,"text":"And you are rarely, if ever, seen by your actual doctor,"},{"time":74113,"text":"just whoever happens to be \nworking at the hospital that day."},{"time":77280,"text":"So we go in for a stress test and after 20 minutes"},{"time":80026,"text":"the doctor comes out and he says,"},{"time":83524,"text":"\"Your baby is under stress, we need to induce you.\""},{"time":89079,"text":"Now, as a statistician, what's my response?"},{"time":93698,"text":"Show me the data!"},{"time":97370,"text":"So then he proceeds to tell us"},{"time":100072,"text":"the baby's heart rate trace went from 18 minutes,"},{"time":102497,"text":"the baby's heart rate was in the normal zone"},{"time":104468,"text":"and for two minutes it was in what appeared to be"},{"time":107421,"text":"my heart rate zone and I said,"},{"time":111131,"text":"\"Is it possible that maybe this was my heart rate?"},{"time":113497,"text":"I was moving around a little bit,"},{"time":115492,"text":"it's hard to lay still on your back,"},{"time":117790,"text":"41 weeks pregnant for 20 minutes."},{"time":120308,"text":"Maybe it was shifting around.\""},{"time":122481,"text":"He said, \"Well, we don't want to take any chances.\""},{"time":127457,"text":"I said okay."},{"time":128717,"text":"I said, \"What if I was at 36 weeks"},{"time":130436,"text":"with this same data?"},{"time":132245,"text":"Would your decision be to induce?\""},{"time":136124,"text":"\"Well, no, I would wait until you were at least"},{"time":139692,"text":"38 weeks, but you are almost 42,"},{"time":141702,"text":"there is no reason to leave that baby inside,"},{"time":143709,"text":"let's get you a room.\""},{"time":145660,"text":"I said, \"Well, why don't we just do it again?"},{"time":152241,"text":"We can collect more data."},{"time":153962,"text":"I can try to be really still for 20 minutes."},{"time":156373,"text":"We can average the two and see"},{"time":159056,"text":"what that means. (Laughter)"},{"time":161738,"text":"And he goes,"},{"time":165385,"text":"\"Ma'am, I just don't want you to have a miscarriage.\""},{"time":172434,"text":"That makes three of us."},{"time":175566,"text":"And then he says,"},{"time":176720,"text":"\"Your chances of having a miscarriage double"},{"time":180838,"text":"when you go past your due date. Let's get you a room.\""},{"time":184605,"text":"Wow. So now as a statistician, what's my response?"},{"time":190892,"text":"Show me the data!"},{"time":192240,"text":"Dude, you're talking chances,"},{"time":193445,"text":"I do chances all day long, tell me all about chances."},{"time":195701,"text":"Let's talk chances. (Laughter)"},{"time":197523,"text":"Let's talk chances."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199488,"text":"So I say, \"Okay, great."},{"time":200689,"text":"Do I go from a 30-percent \nchance to a 60-percent chance?"},{"time":204590,"text":"Where are we here with this miscarriage thing?"},{"time":207141,"text":"And he goes, \"Not quite, but it doubles,"},{"time":210437,"text":"and we really just want what's best for the baby.\""},{"time":215419,"text":"Undaunted, I try a different angle."},{"time":217582,"text":"I said, \"Okay, out of 1,000 full-term pregnant women,"},{"time":223089,"text":"how many of them are going to miscarry"},{"time":225616,"text":"just before their due date?"},{"time":227411,"text":"And then he looks at me and looks at Donald,"},{"time":230259,"text":"and he goes, about one in 1,000."},{"time":234962,"text":"I said, \"Okay, so of those 1,000 women, how many"},{"time":237792,"text":"are going to miscarry just after their due date?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":242650,"text":"\"About two.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":246222,"text":"I said, \"Okay, so you are telling me that my chances"},{"time":248266,"text":"go from a 0.1-percent chance"},{"time":252213,"text":"to a 0.2-percent chance.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":256459,"text":"Okay, so at this point the data is not convincing us"},{"time":258757,"text":"that we need to be induced,"},{"time":260385,"text":"and so then we proceed to have a conversation"},{"time":262334,"text":"about how inductions lead to a higher rate"},{"time":264982,"text":"of Cesarean sections, and if at all \npossible we'd like to avoid that."},{"time":268973,"text":"And then I said,"},{"time":270225,"text":"\"And I really don't think my due date is accurate.\""},{"time":273105,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":275705,"text":"And so this really stunned him"},{"time":278445,"text":"and he looked sort of puzzled"},{"time":280095,"text":"and I said, \"You may not know this,"},{"time":282227,"text":"but pregnancy due dates are calculated"},{"time":283808,"text":"assuming that you have a standard 28-day cycle,"},{"time":286346,"text":"and my cycle ranges —"},{"time":287748,"text":"sometimes it's 27, sometimes it's up to 38 —"},{"time":291295,"text":"and I have been collecting the data to prove it."},{"time":294449,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":298233,"text":"And so we ended up leaving the hospital \nthat day without being induced."},{"time":304070,"text":"We actually had to sign a waiver \nto walk out of the hospital."},{"time":310263,"text":"And I'm not advocating that you not listen to your doctors,"},{"time":313951,"text":"because even with our first child,"},{"time":315869,"text":"we were induced at 38 weeks; cervical fluid was low."},{"time":319511,"text":"I'm not anti-medical intervention."},{"time":321969,"text":"But why were confident to leave that day?"},{"time":324833,"text":"Well, we had data that told a different story."},{"time":328483,"text":"We had been collecting data for six years."},{"time":333491,"text":"I had this temperature data,"},{"time":335789,"text":"and it told a different story."},{"time":337064,"text":"In fact, we could probably pretty \naccurately estimate conception."},{"time":344477,"text":"Yeah, that's a story you want to tell"},{"time":346379,"text":"at your kid's wedding reception. (Laughter)"},{"time":349631,"text":"I remember like it was yesterday."},{"time":353324,"text":"My temperature was a sizzling 97.8 degrees"},{"time":355965,"text":"as I stared into your father's eyes. (Laughter)"},{"time":360119,"text":"Oh, yeah. Twenty-two more years, we're telling that story."},{"time":366931,"text":"But we were confident to leave \nbecause we had been collecting data."},{"time":369984,"text":"Now, what does that data look like?"},{"time":371590,"text":"Here's a standard chart"},{"time":374427,"text":"of a woman's waking body temperature"},{"time":377729,"text":"during the course of a cycle."},{"time":379246,"text":"So from the beginning of the menstrual cycle"},{"time":380699,"text":"till the beginning of the next."},{"time":382051,"text":"You'll see that the temperature is not random."},{"time":384872,"text":"Clearly there is a low pattern"},{"time":386936,"text":"at the beginning of her cycle"},{"time":388935,"text":"and then you see this jump and then a higher"},{"time":391434,"text":"set of temperatures at the end of her cycle."},{"time":393712,"text":"So what's happening here?"},{"time":395133,"text":"What is that data telling you?"},{"time":397739,"text":"Well, ladies, at the beginning of our cycle,"},{"time":400438,"text":"the hormone estrogen is dominant and that estrogen"},{"time":403780,"text":"causes a suppression of your body temperature."},{"time":407589,"text":"And at ovulation, your body releases an egg"},{"time":411126,"text":"and progesterone takes over, pro-gestation."},{"time":416141,"text":"And so your body heats up in anticipation"},{"time":418493,"text":"of housing this new little fertilized egg."},{"time":422279,"text":"So why this temperature jump?"},{"time":425011,"text":"Well, think about when a bird sits on her eggs."},{"time":428687,"text":"Why is she sitting on them?"},{"time":430153,"text":"She wants to keep them warm,"},{"time":432090,"text":"protect them and keep them warm."},{"time":433594,"text":"Ladies, this is exactly what our bodies do every month,"},{"time":435865,"text":"they heat up in anticipation"},{"time":437956,"text":"of keeping a new little life warm."},{"time":441092,"text":"And if nothing happens, if you are not pregnant,"},{"time":444022,"text":"then estrogen takes back over and \nthat cycle starts all over again."},{"time":448564,"text":"But if you do get pregnant, sometimes you"},{"time":450511,"text":"actually see another shift in your temperatures"},{"time":453055,"text":"and it stays elevated for those whole nine months."},{"time":456342,"text":"That's why you see those pregnant \nwomen just sweating and hot,"},{"time":459667,"text":"because their temperatures are high."},{"time":463045,"text":"Here's a chart that we had about three or four years ago."},{"time":467414,"text":"We were really very excited about this chart."},{"time":469434,"text":"You'll see the low temperature level"},{"time":471970,"text":"and then a shift and for about five days,"},{"time":475012,"text":"that's about the time it takes for the egg to travel"},{"time":477471,"text":"down the fallopian tube and implant,"},{"time":479918,"text":"and then you see those temperatures \nstart to go up a little bit."},{"time":483559,"text":"And in fact, we had a second temperature shift,"},{"time":486772,"text":"confirmed with a pregnancy test \nthat were indeed pregnant"},{"time":490832,"text":"with our first child, very exciting."},{"time":493913,"text":"Until a couple of days later"},{"time":495944,"text":"I saw some spotting and then I noticed heavy blood flow,"},{"time":500885,"text":"and we had in fact had an early stage miscarriage."},{"time":505244,"text":"Had I not been taking my temperature"},{"time":509114,"text":"I really would have just thought \nmy period was late that month,"},{"time":513012,"text":"but we actually had data to show"},{"time":514820,"text":"that we had miscarried this baby,"},{"time":517447,"text":"and even though this data revealed a really"},{"time":519280,"text":"unfortunate event in our lives,"},{"time":521064,"text":"it was information that we could then take to our doctor."},{"time":523531,"text":"So if there was a fertility issue or some problem,"},{"time":526159,"text":"I had data to show:"},{"time":527414,"text":"Look, we got pregnant, our temperature shifted,"},{"time":529761,"text":"we somehow lost this baby."},{"time":531445,"text":"What is it that we can do to help prevent this problem?"},{"time":534805,"text":"And it's not just about temperatures"},{"time":538326,"text":"and it's not just about fertility;"},{"time":541067,"text":"we can use data about our bodies to tell us a lot of things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544955,"text":"For instance, did you know that taking \nyour temperature can tell you a lot"},{"time":548785,"text":"about the condition of your thyroid?"},{"time":550924,"text":"So, your thyroid works a lot like \nthe thermostat in your house."},{"time":554939,"text":"There is an optimal temperature \nthat you want in your house;"},{"time":557157,"text":"you set your thermostat."},{"time":558681,"text":"When it gets too cold in the house,\nyour thermostat kicks in"},{"time":561175,"text":"and says, \"Hey, we need to blow some heat around.\""},{"time":564393,"text":"Or if it gets too hot, your thermostat"},{"time":566062,"text":"registers, \"Turn the A.C. on. Cool us off.\""},{"time":569619,"text":"That's exactly how your thyroid works in your body."},{"time":573416,"text":"Your thyroid tries to keep an optimal temperature"},{"time":576116,"text":"for your body."},{"time":577144,"text":"If it gets too cold, your thyroid \nsays, \"Hey, we need to heat up.\""},{"time":579626,"text":"If it gets too hot, your thyroid cools you down."},{"time":582814,"text":"But what happens when your \nthyroid is not functioning well?"},{"time":587220,"text":"When it doesn't function, then it shows up"},{"time":589587,"text":"in your body temperatures,"},{"time":590773,"text":"they tend to be lower than normal or very erratic."},{"time":593428,"text":"And so by collecting this data"},{"time":594698,"text":"you can find out information about your thyroid."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597685,"text":"Now, what is it, if you had a thyroid \nproblem and you went to the doctor,"},{"time":601249,"text":"your doctor would actually test the amount of"},{"time":603682,"text":"thyroid stimulating hormone in your blood."},{"time":606620,"text":"Fine. But the problem with that test is"},{"time":610803,"text":"it doesn't tell you how active the hormone is in your body."},{"time":613568,"text":"So you might have a lot of hormone present,"},{"time":615617,"text":"but it might not be actively working to regulate"},{"time":617365,"text":"your body temperature."},{"time":618613,"text":"So just by collecting your temperature every day,"},{"time":620362,"text":"you get information about the condition of your thyroid."},{"time":623982,"text":"So, what if you don't want to take \nyour temperature every day?"},{"time":626463,"text":"I advocate that you do,"},{"time":628021,"text":"but there are tons of other things you could take."},{"time":629876,"text":"You could take your blood pressure, \nyou could take your weight —"},{"time":632681,"text":"yeah, who's excited about"},{"time":634271,"text":"taking their weight every day? (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":637808,"text":"Early on in our marriage, Donald had a stuffy nose"},{"time":642599,"text":"and he had been taking a slew of medications"},{"time":645719,"text":"to try to relieve his stuffy nose, to no avail."},{"time":649718,"text":"And so, that night he comes and \nhe wakes me up and he says,"},{"time":653957,"text":"\"Honey, I can't breath out of my nose.\""},{"time":657764,"text":"And I roll over and I look, and I said, \n\"Well, can you breath out of your mouth?\""},{"time":662582,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":664060,"text":"And he goes, \"Yes, but I can't breath out of my nose!\""},{"time":671140,"text":"And so like any good wife, I rush him"},{"time":674160,"text":"to the emergency room"},{"time":675995,"text":"at 2 o'clock in the morning."},{"time":678427,"text":"And the whole time I'm driving and I'm thinking,"},{"time":681897,"text":"you can't die on me now."},{"time":684746,"text":"We just got married,"},{"time":686916,"text":"people will think I killed you! (Laughter)"},{"time":691374,"text":"And so, we get to the emergency \nroom, and the nurse sees us,"},{"time":695047,"text":"and he can't breath out of his nose, and so"},{"time":697668,"text":"she brings us to the back and the doctor says,"},{"time":699751,"text":"\"What seems to be the problem?\" and \nhe goes, \"I can't breath out of my nose.\""},{"time":702940,"text":"And he said, \"You can't breath out of your nose?"},{"time":704989,"text":"No, but he can breath out of his mouth. (Laughter)"},{"time":710866,"text":"He takes a step back and he looks at both of us"},{"time":713508,"text":"and he says \"Sir, I think I know the problem."},{"time":717374,"text":"You're having a heart attack."},{"time":718810,"text":"I'm going to order an EKG and a CAT scan"},{"time":720861,"text":"for you immediately.\""},{"time":724203,"text":"And we are thinking,"},{"time":725831,"text":"no, no, no. It's not a heart attack. He can breathe,"},{"time":728771,"text":"just out of his mouth. No, no, no, no, no."},{"time":733768,"text":"And so we go back and forth with this doctor"},{"time":736031,"text":"because we think this is the incorrect diagnosis,"},{"time":738509,"text":"and he's like, \"No really, it'll be fine, just calm down.\""},{"time":742461,"text":"And I'm thinking, how do you calm down? \nBut I don't think he's having a heart attack."},{"time":746380,"text":"And so fortunately for us, this \ndoctor was at the end of the shift."},{"time":749621,"text":"So this new doctor comes in, he sees us clearly"},{"time":752536,"text":"distraught, with a husband who can't breath"},{"time":755537,"text":"out of his nose. (Laughter)"},{"time":758639,"text":"And he starts asking us questions."},{"time":761425,"text":"He says, \"Well, do you two exercise?\""},{"time":766305,"text":"We ride our bikes, we go to the gym occasionally."},{"time":773378,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":775031,"text":"We move around."},{"time":777896,"text":"And he says, \"What were you doing \njust before you came here?\""},{"time":780559,"text":"I'm thinking, I was sleeping, honestly."},{"time":783271,"text":"But okay, what was Donald doing just before?"},{"time":786102,"text":"So Donald goes into this slew \nof medications he was taking."},{"time":789650,"text":"He lists, \"I took this decongestant \nand then I took this nasal spray,\""},{"time":792612,"text":"and then all of a sudden a lightbulb goes off and he says,"},{"time":794615,"text":"\"Oh! You should never mix this \ndecongestant with this nasal spray."},{"time":798242,"text":"Clogs you up every time. Here, take this one instead.\""},{"time":801059,"text":"He gives us a prescription."},{"time":803325,"text":"We're looking at each other, and I looked at the doctor,"},{"time":805315,"text":"and I said, \"Why is it that it seems like you"},{"time":807541,"text":"were able to accurately diagnose his condition,"},{"time":809952,"text":"but this previous doctor wanted to order"},{"time":812168,"text":"an EKG and a CAT scan?\""},{"time":814674,"text":"And he looks at us and says,"},{"time":817281,"text":"\"Well, when a 350-pound man walks in the \nemergency room and says he can't breath,"},{"time":821499,"text":"you assume he's having a heart attack"},{"time":823263,"text":"and you ask questions later.\""},{"time":827212,"text":"Now, emergency room doctors are \ntrained to make decisions quickly,"},{"time":832932,"text":"but not always accurately."},{"time":835023,"text":"And so had we had some information"},{"time":836572,"text":"about our heart health to share with him,"},{"time":838966,"text":"maybe we would have gotten a \nbetter diagnosis the first time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":842741,"text":"I want you to consider the following chart,"},{"time":844973,"text":"of systolic blood pressure measurements"},{"time":846927,"text":"from October 2010 to July 2012."},{"time":850999,"text":"You'll see that these measurements start"},{"time":852692,"text":"in the prehypertension/hypertension zone,"},{"time":856360,"text":"but over about the course of a year and a half"},{"time":858946,"text":"they move into the normal zone."},{"time":861591,"text":"This is about the heart rate of a healthy 16-year-old."},{"time":865700,"text":"What story is this data telling you?"},{"time":869731,"text":"Obviously it's the data from someone"},{"time":872612,"text":"who's made a drastic transformation,"},{"time":875285,"text":"and fortunately for us, that person \nhappens to be here today."},{"time":880443,"text":"So that 350-pound guy that walked \ninto the emergency room with me"},{"time":884697,"text":"is now an even sexier and healthier"},{"time":887669,"text":"225-pound guy, and that's his blood pressure trace."},{"time":894357,"text":"So over the course of that year and a half"},{"time":897818,"text":"Donald's eating changed"},{"time":899387,"text":"and our exercise regimen changed,"},{"time":901378,"text":"and his heart rate responded,"},{"time":904168,"text":"his blood pressure responded to that change"},{"time":905670,"text":"that he made in his body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":907969,"text":"So what's the take-home message"},{"time":909947,"text":"that I want you to leave with today?"},{"time":913661,"text":"By taking ownership of your data just like we've done,"},{"time":918035,"text":"just by taking this daily measurements about yourself,"},{"time":921982,"text":"you become the expert on your body."},{"time":924491,"text":"You become the authority."},{"time":926493,"text":"It's not hard to do."},{"time":928916,"text":"You don't have to have a Ph.D. in statistics"},{"time":930836,"text":"to be an expert in yourself."},{"time":932168,"text":"You don't have to have a medical degree"},{"time":933609,"text":"to be your body's expert."},{"time":935735,"text":"Medical doctors, they're experts on the population,"},{"time":939154,"text":"but you are the expert on yourself."},{"time":941432,"text":"And so when two of you come together,"},{"time":943342,"text":"when two experts come together,"},{"time":945312,"text":"the two of you are able to make a better decision"},{"time":948107,"text":"than just your doctor alone."},{"time":950107,"text":"Now that you understand the power of information"},{"time":953874,"text":"that you can get through personal data collection,"},{"time":955745,"text":"I'd like you all to stand and raise your right hand."},{"time":959414,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":961973,"text":"Yes, get it up."},{"time":966771,"text":"I challenge you to take ownership of your data."},{"time":973679,"text":"And today, I hereby confer upon you"},{"time":977241,"text":"a TEDx associate's degree in elementary statistics"},{"time":981586,"text":"with a concentration in time-dependent data analysis"},{"time":986030,"text":"with all the rights and privileges appertaining thereto."},{"time":989743,"text":"And so the next time you are in your doctor's office,"},{"time":993219,"text":"as newly inducted statisticians,"},{"time":996410,"text":"what should always be your response?"},{"time":998920,"text":"Audience: Show me the data! \nTalithia Williams: I can't hear you!"},{"time":1000752,"text":"Audience: Show me the data!"},{"time":1002520,"text":"TW: One more time!"},{"time":1003828,"text":"Audience: Show me the data!"},{"time":1005367,"text":"TW: Show me the data."},{"time":1006549,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":1009570,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}